messages.content:
What is the name of the HTML element that is used to create a paragraph?
a.
&lt;para&gt;
b.
&lt;p&gt;
c.
&lt;paragraph&gt;
d.
All of the above.

Which HTML element is used to add an image to a web page?
a.
&lt;img&gt;
b.
&lt;image&gt;
c.
None of the above
d.
&lt;picture&gt;

What is an example of a use case for the <abbr> tag?
a.
All of the above
b.
To display the abbreviation "HTML" as &lt;abbr title="HyperText Markup Language"&gt;HTML&lt;/abbr&gt;
c.
To display the abbreviation "CSS" as &lt;abbr title="Cascading Style Sheets"&gt;CSS&lt;/abbr&gt;
d.
To display the acronym "HTTP" as &lt;abbr title="HyperText Transfer Protocol"&gt;HTTP&lt;/abbr&gt;
